title: SikkerAPI
description: Import IP reputation indicators from SikkerAPI's TAXII 2.1 feed into OpenCTI. Data is sourced from a globally distributed honeypot network capturing real attacker behavior. Includes confidence scoring, MITRE ATT&CK mappings, behavioral labels, and kill chain phases.
short_description: IP reputation indicators from SikkerAPI honeypot network via TAXII 2.1.
